dc_title_s: Roads and ROW Jefferson County, WI 2022
dc_description_s: This data represents roads (2022) and Right of Ways (ROW) (2020) for Jefferson County, Wisconsin, and includes the layers 'JEFFERSON_ROADS_2022' and 'JEFFERSON_ROW_2022'. While the roads data layer is current to 2022, the Right of Ways (ROW) data has not been updated since 2020. [Roads: Jefferson County Road Center Lines L = Local Road C = County Road S = State Road P = Private Road I = Interstate F = Federal Road. ROW: The parcel line layer delineates parcel features such as ownership boundaries, roads, water features, easements and others that affect property ownership interests.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.
